<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>413</hymn_number>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw nang Zion, Khua zakip ah Pathian cu, Ceunak a si, tiah rianrang in
 chim hna, Miphun kip sertu Pathian nih mui chungin, Thlarau pakhat tlau a
 siang lo tiah chim.

[C1]
   Lung-lawmhnak Thawngtha, daihnak, luatnak, Khamhbawi Jesuh tlanhnak
   thawngtha thanter tuah.

[V2]
 Zohhmanh sualnak, Thonginn a ummi chungah, Thong zeizat dah,
 hrengkhenh in a um rih, Khamhtu thihnak aho chimtu ngei loin, An co hnga
 nunnak kong kha an thei lo.

[C2]
   Lung-lawmhnak Thawngtha, daihnak, luatnak, Khamhbawi Jesuh tlanhnak
   thawngtha thanter tuah.

[V3]
 Holh phunkip le, Miphun zakip sinah khan, Pathian cu dawtnak a si,
 tiah thanh hna, A tlaumi khamh awkah van in a rung tum, Nun ro kan co
 nakhnga thihnak a in.

[C3]
   Lung-lawmhnak Thawngtha, daihnak, luatnak, Khamhbawi Jesuh tlanhnak
   thawngtha thanter tuah.

[V4]
 Sunparnak thawng chim ah na fapale cu, Na chawhlawn he khua zakip ah
 thlah hna, Annih caah zungzal in thla va cam ko, Na liammi vialte Jesuh
 an cham lai.

[C4]
   Lung-lawmhnak Thawngtha, daihnak, luatnak, Khamhbawi Jesuh tlanhnak
   thawngtha thanter tuah.</lyrics>
<title>MAW ZION, KHULRANG TUAH CH413</title>
</song>